      "text": "Thompson describes one school system’s journey towards a process of creative discovery that involved rapid trial and error with the understanding that even disappointment involves learning. This would be the “*hacking*” component of his agile mindset, using the kindest interpretation of that term, one rooted again in Boston’s MIT.\n"
    },
